                  <persName role="owner" corresp="PRS0000">Qäňňazmač Gäbrä Ḥǝywät is mentioned as the donor in Additio 1. He and members of his family are mentioned in supplication formulas: Gäbrä Ḥǝywät (e.g., fols. 10vb, 27vb, 29va, 31ra, 32ra, 43ra, 50ra, 59ra, 74va), Wälättä Maryam (e.g., fols. 27vb, 29va, 30vb, 31ra, 31vb, 35va, 44ra, 61va, 74va), his wife Wälättä Śǝllase (e.g., fols. 27vb, 29va, 70va, 73ra), Täsfa Mikaʾel (e.g., fols. 27vb, 70rb, 74ra), Wälättä  Mikaʾel (e.g., fols. 27vb, 74ra, 74rb, 74va). &#xD;
Further nine names are mentioned in the concluding supplication formula on fol. 74vb.</persName>
